y affair for Australia's most famous paddling family, the Fox's, after Jess's sister Noemie earned Australia an Olympic quota spot in the kayak cross in Prague.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.333848479447933e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999996220963826, \"rank\": 2.3380710033981055e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 450, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999996220963826, \"rank\": 2.3380710033981055e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"score\": 0.999998682639629, \"rank\": 9.998130462723624e-07, \"text\": \"Prague\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paddle Photography\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"a real family affair\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"Jess's sister\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"Noemie\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic quota spot\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"the kayak cross\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result all but confirms the younger of the Fox sisters a spot at the Paris Games, alongside Jess.\", \"from\": 513, 