\" Fox said.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9970692881653902, \"rank\": 0.002182992533178411, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a long journey\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel so grateful to have had the most incredible support team here with me and to be able to celebrate it and join the Australian Olympic team, and join my sister, it's so incredible and I am so happy.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.5919814341534154e-13, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most incredible support team\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"my sister\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie Fox is all but certain to join her sister in Paris.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.308051981529536e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sister\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Paddle Photography) \\\"The semifinal with the reigning world champion, past world champion and European medallist was probably the hardest thing.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paddle Photography\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"The semifinal\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the reigning world champion\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"past world champion\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"European medallist\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest thing\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So once I got through that and I was in the final, I was just wanting to enjoy it and not come last, and that's what I did.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox, who will appear at her first Olympic Games, is the latest in a paddling dynasty that started with her father - British paddler Richard Fox, a 10-time world champion and bronze medallist at the 1992 Olympics - and her mother, Myriam Fox-Jerusalmi, who won a bronze medal at the 1996 Games for France.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9970692881653902, \"rank\": 0.002182992533178411, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9988937042257774, \"rank\": 0.0010833146949394785, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unit